## Critical Bug Found

**`eventServerResponse` expects an event object, NOT a string!**

```typescript
// WRONG (current code in orderDetail.service.ts)
eventServerResponse('ORDER_DETAIL_SUCCESS' as never);

// CORRECT (how other services do it)
eventServerResponse(ANALYTICS_EVENTS.ORDER_DETAIL_SUCCESS);
```

The `ANALYTICS_EVENTS.ORDER_DETAIL_SUCCESS` and `ANALYTICS_EVENTS.ORDER_DETAIL_ERROR` constants were **defined but never imported or used**. The `as never` cast was added to silence TypeScript, hiding the bug.

